Date: Mon, 27 Apr 2026 10:18:09 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?ci(akakce):=20cron=20devre=20disi=20=E2=80=94?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20BIM=20marketfiyati=20canli,=20OCR=20pipeline=20kullanilmiyor?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Akakce broşür OCR pipeline'inin ürettigi extracted_products.json kimse
tarafından okunmuyordu (bim_akakce.py registry'de yok, orphan). BIM
artik marketfiyati'dan canli besleniyor (parsers/bim.py, ~725 ürün/sweep).
Cron'u kapatip workflow'u yedek olarak biraktik — manuel workflow_dispatch
hala mumkun, schedule yorum olarak kaldı.
---
 .github/workflows/akakce-actueller-feed.yml | 9 +++++++--
 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/.github/workflows/akakce-actueller-feed.yml b/.github/workflows/akakce-actueller-feed.yml
index abf3c32..c1cb31d 100644
--- a/.github/workflows/akakce-actueller-feed.yml
+++ b/.github/workflows/akakce-actueller-feed.yml
@@ -34,8 +34,13 @@ on:
     paths:
       - ".github/workflows/akakce-actueller-feed.yml"
       - "tools/akakce_worker/**"
-  schedule:
-    - cron: "0 5 * * *"
+  # 2026-04-26: cron devre disi. BIM artik marketfiyati'dan canli besleniyor
+  # (parsers/bim.py); akakce broşür OCR pipeline'inin urettigi extracted_products.json
+  # registry'de okunmuyor (bim_akakce.py orphan). Workflow yedek olarak korunuyor;
+  # broşür akisi yeniden gerekirse schedule'i geri ac:
+  #   schedule:
+  #     - cron: "0 5 * * *"
+  # workflow_dispatch ile manuel trigger her zaman mumkun.
 
 jobs:
   build-actueller-feed:
-- 
2.34.1

